    "It would be an interesting research direction to extend these results from 1-dimensional to multidimensional scenarios.",
    "Multi-dimensional learned indexWe investigate data layouts adopted by different learned indexes in Sect. 3.1.",
    "Then, we develop an index taxonomy in Sect. 3.2 and overview indexes in each category in Sect.",
    "Table 1 highlights key technical features of existing multi-dimensional learned indexes.",
    "Data layoutData layout specifies how an index organizes multidimensional data in storage (i.e., disk or memory), forming the basis of subsequent learned index taxonomy."
